at.irian.ankor.ref.match.pattern

Class RefPatternBaseListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • at.irian.ankor.ref.match.pattern.RefPatternBaseListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RefPatternListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener

    public class RefPatternBaseListener
extends Object
implements RefPatternListener
    This class provides an empty implementation of RefPatternListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
